  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will assess, over a 4-week treatment period, the safety and efficacy of the
      addition of sitagliptin to metformin in participants with type 2 diabetes mellitus (T2DM) who
      failed to achieve glycemic control on metformin monotherapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
